&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Instawork is on a mission to create meaningful economic opportunities for skilled hourly professionals in communities around the globe. Our AI-powered labor marketplace helps local businesses scale, and enables global technology companies to push the frontiers of robotics and AI. Backed by world-class investors like Benchmark, Spark Capital, Craft Ventures, Greylock, Y Combinator, and others, we’re looking for exceptional talent to reimagine the way the world works.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;The future of hourly work has arrived, and we are looking for a top-performing Account Executive to help lead the charge. Instawork is the #1 marketplace connecting businesses with skilled hourly workers, with 10M+ workers across 40+ markets in North America. Backed by Benchmark, Greylock, and other world-class investors, we are reinventing how businesses hire, and we are just getting started.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is your chance to sell a product that genuinely changes lives. Our AI-powered platform creates real economic opportunity for workers while solving one of the most pressing challenges businesses face: reliable, on-demand staffing. You will be selling into an expansive and exciting total addressable market, including Major Sports Stadiums, E-commerce brands, major universities, AI companies, and beyond.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a high-impact role for a hunter who thrives on competition, loves to win, and wants to be part of something that matters. You will report to a Sales Manager and play a critical role in driving Instawork’s next phase of growth, on-site 5 days per week in our downtown Chicago office.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+ years of B2B sales experience with a proven, consistent track record of exceeding quota&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A relentless competitor who lives at the top of the leaderboard and will not settle for anything less&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Energized by coaching and obsessed with leveling up your craft&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A true hunter who thrives in fast-paced environments and knows how to build pipeline from scratch through outbound prospecting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluent in a robust sales stack; proficiency in Salesforce, Outreach, and ZoomInfo/Sales Navigator preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sharp negotiator with experience navigating commercial and legal terms to close&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passionate about selling a product that creates real economic opportunity and changes people’s lives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An exceptional communicator who is compelling on the phone, polished on video, and persuasive in person&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience selling into large hospitality or warehousing brands is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own your territory and build high-value partnerships with top partners across Major Sports Stadiums, E-commerce brands, universities, AI companies, and more&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive aggressive outbound prospecting to generate your own pipeline through cold calls, targeted sequences, and creative outreach&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reach executives and key decision makers, delivering compelling and tailored presentations that win&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use a consultative sales approach to show prospects exactly why Instawork is the faster, smarter alternative to legacy staffing solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Close new business over the phone, video, and in-person, then obsess over expanding those accounts from day one&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Negotiate commercial and legal terms with confidence to get deals across the finish line&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver accurate weekly forecasts and own your number&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with sales and operations to ensure customers experience the full power of Instawork’s platform&lt;/li&gt;
