&lt;li&gt;Convince business owners to allow commercial video data collection&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build relationships and close partnerships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hire and manage Field Officers (FOs) and Data Collectors (DCs)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure daily recordings happen smoothly at business locations&lt;/li&gt;
