&lt;li&gt;Vendor onboarding professionals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operations hustlers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Team leaders who can manage field staff&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
