&lt;li&gt;Ownership mindset and high energy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable with travel and field work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work independently without constant supervision&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Earnings &amp;amp; Growth&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;💰 Earn ₹60,000 to ₹4,00,000/month based on:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hours delivered&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Team performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Categories unlocked&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operational consistency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;High performers can grow fast and handle multiple cities/regions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Work Details&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Location: Across India&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mode: Field + Operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High travel involved&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Success in This Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will succeed if you can:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build strong business partnerships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run high-performing field teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver consistent daily output&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operate like a mini business owner&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;🚀 If you are street-smart, aggressive in the field, and hungry to build something big, this role is for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Our Values&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
