&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Instawork is on a mission to create meaningful economic opportunities for skilled hourly professionals in communities around the globe. Our AI-powered labor marketplace helps local businesses scale, and enables global technology companies to push the frontiers of robotics and AI. Backed by world-class investors like Benchmark, Spark Capital, Craft Ventures, Greylock, Y Combinator, and others, we’re looking for exceptional talent to reimagine the way the world works.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About IRL&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Researchers at UC Berkeley have identified a “100,000-year data gap” - the gulf between what trained AI language models and what physical robots actually have to learn from. Closing that gap is the defining infrastructure challenge of the physical AI era. IRL is Instawork’s answer to it. We deploy skilled workers into real commercial and residential environments - kitchens, warehouses, hotel floors, homes - to capture the high-fidelity task data that the world’s leading Robotics labs use to train their foundation models. Read more&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://x.com/sumirmeghani/status/2044707303262237129&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Commercial Field Sales is responsible for onboarding commercial businesses onto the Instawork data collection platform, managing a team of Field Officers, and ensuring maximum recording hours across all active locations. The role combines business development, team management, and operational execution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A Data Captain has the opportunity to earn incentives up to ₹1,00,000 per week.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify, pitch, and onboard commercial businesses (retail shops, kitchens, construction sites, workshops) for egocentric video data collection&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure weekly hours targets are met across all onboarded businesses to hit slab bonuses&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage Field Officers who are stationed at business locations to supervise recording&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate device allocation with the office — ensure the right number of devices reach each location&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain the business pipeline in the tracking sheet (Commercial Conversion Responses)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure business owners understand the payout structure and are motivated to maximize recording hours per device&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business Development &amp;amp; Onboarding&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Visit 8-10 commercial businesses daily to pitch the data collection opportunity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver the standard pitch: &quot;We pay you per hour. Your team wears a small phone while doing their normal work. We record for 2-3 days, pay you, and leave.&quot;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Explain the business payout slabs: ₹0 for under 2 hours per device, ₹200/hr for 2-4 hours, ₹600 bonus at 4 hours, ₹350/hr above 4 hours&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handle common objections (what&#39;s it for, how long, is it legal, rate negotiation)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Get the agreement signed on the spot&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Log every business in the Google Sheet immediately — Field Officer gets auto-assigned&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Field Officer Management&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Each Data Captain manages multiple Field Officers stationed at different business locations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track which locations are actively recording and how many device-hours are being logged daily&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Call Field Officers at slow locations — the #1 failure mode is collectors taking breaks and hours staying low&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure FOs are pushing for 6+ hours per device per day at every location&lt;/li&gt;
